{"tid":1742760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[另類角度] 想分享下普羅大眾手足對今次罷工既睇法","createTime":"2019-11-21T02:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T11:46:01.000Z","uid":10176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2064fdfe908a56592eaef1c2dc7a8736969b7353","tid":1742760,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:18:21.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\n普羅大眾手足=唔上連登既手足<br />\n<br />\n前幾日同一個唔上連登既朋友傾計<br />\n講到今次罷工<br />\n佢話今次罷工比起上次8月罷工黎講<br />\n有一個好大既分別<br />\n就係今次罷工宣傳不足<br />\n上次8月罷工果陣<br />\n文宣鋪天蓋地咁宣傳<br />\n最緊要既係<br />\n唔淨係局限於連登<br />\n係facebook, whatsapp都瘋傳會罷工<br />\n令到一班唔上連登, 但又想響應罷工既手足有定心理準備<br />\n知道有罷工依單野<br />\n咁先至可以迎合到 (始終都係要被動罷工先得, 希望港豬們有朝一日會主動罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n今次係有d急<br />\n但做到咁既成效<br />\n手足們真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果想下次再黎多次黎明行動<br />\n事前準備宣傳俾班被動港豬<br />\n等多d港豬有心理定行動準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令到行動成效最大化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家加油!"},{"pid":"bc803ffa20964366643b73e1014ff8e514d1265b","tid":1742760,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4c5076dc115cf26114e3906fca564dc53b583c","tid":1742760,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c17a57490650d3cf22a62550c06b65a02aae34","tid":1742760,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc4e63a00f2e2f6a99a7ed1fea0cd7dc55ed9ba","tid":1742760,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"